de.ityx.mediatrix.data

Class Keyword

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.AbstractKeywordCategory
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.Keyword
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Filter.KeywordAdapter

    public class Keyword
extends AbstractKeywordCategory
    The operator can insert the keywords e.g. to the question. They are used to create e.g. reports or search for the questions. are used for subsequent classification and fast search of processed emails.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
